@Node Registration



                        	@{u}@{b}Registration@{ub}@{uu}


  If you like this software, please contact me and I will continue to develope it.

  From Gir version 0.4, I decided to make Gir shareware. I hope to make a

  a little money this way.

  I don't have time and money for programing for nothing.

  Feel free to contact me.



                                 Prices-


  If you send me 5 US$,  I'll send  you the keyfile for Gir and you get rid of

  the stupid onscreen messages.

  If you pay another 5 US$ I'll update your key and all future features will be free.

  So if you send me 10 US$ (or more :- ), I'll send to you key for Gir and all

  new features in future versions will be free for you .



                               How do you register  ?


  All you need is to send me file "my_key" from Gir directory. This file is

  produced by Gir, and will be your personal hardware serial number.

  So, if you pay 5/10 US$ I'll send you "key" file and you will get rid of

  the stupid messages.

  Send me the file "my_key" which you'll find in the GIR05 directory

  and all your data by email, or on a floppy disk by mail to my address:

  @{"  Author  " Link Author}

  For the moment, you must send money only in _safely_ mail.

  If you want to pay via the bank please first contact the author.

  If you don't know how to send binary file with email contact me first by email.

  You must send these data:


        Name:    ____________________________________

        Email:   ____________________________________

        Address: ____________________________________


                 ------------------------------------


        Country:____________________________________

        Tel:    ____________________________________

        OS:     2.0, 3.0, 3.1, pOS _________________

        CPU:    68020, 68030, 68040, 68060, 603, 604

        MHz:    ____________________________________

        FPU:    68881, 6882, 603, 604 ...

        I pay to you  ______ US$ (DM ...)





  If you don't want to register, you may use the version with the stupid messages.

  I'm planning to include MPEG compression to GIR in future versions but this

  is not a small task and don't expect this for tomorrow .

  If you want to speedup the project, however, AND help author send 10 US $ ( ~17 DM )

  in >>safety<< mail.

  If someone wants to pay on my bank account please contact me first .

  Sorry, but I really need the money.




                          @{"  Author  " Link Author}


